xt-olive-700 transition\" aria-label=\"複製連結\"><svg viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" class=\"w-4 h-4 fill-none stroke-current stroke-2\"><path d=\"M10 13a5 5 0 0 0 7.54.54l3-3a5 5 0 0 0-7.07-7.07l-1.72 1.71\"></path><path d=\"M14 11a5 5 0 0 0-7.54-.54l-3 3a5 5 0 0 0 7.07 7.07l1.71-1.71\"></path></svg></button></div></div></div></section><section class=\"bg-olive-50 py-14 px-6\"><div class=\"max-w-4xl mx-auto\"><h2 class=\"text-xl font-bold text-olive-800 mb-6\">同欄目精選文章</h2><div class=\"grid md:grid-cols-3 gap-5\"><a class=\"group\" href=\"/blog/olive-oil-storage-guide-2026/\"><article class=\"bg-white rounded-xl shadow-sm hover:shadow-md transition-all overflow-hidden\"><div class=\"relative h-36 overflow-hidden\"><img alt=\"橄欖油保存完全指南：五個你一直做錯的儲存習慣，正在偷走你的健康投資 — 知橄生活 Olive Wisdom\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" data-nimg=\"fill\" class=\"object-cover group-hover:scale-105 transition-transform duration-300\" style=\"position:absolute;height:100%;width:100%;left:0;top:0;right:0;bottom:0;color:transparent\" src=\"https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1558618666-fcd25c85cd64?w=1200&amp;auto=format&amp;fit=crop&amp;q=80\"/></div><div class=\"p-4\"><h3 class=\"text-sm font-bold text-olive-800 line-clamp-2 group-hover:text-olive-600 transition-colors\">橄欖油保存完全指南：五個你一直做錯的儲存習慣，正在偷走你的健康投資</h3><p class=\"text-xs text-gray-400 mt-2\">8<!-- --> 分鐘閱讀</p></div></article></a><a class=\"group\" href=\"/blog/mediterranean-diet-anti-aging-2026/\"><article class=\"bg-white rounded-xl shadow-sm hover:shadow-md transition-all overflow-hidden\"><div class=\"relative h-36 overflow-hidden\"><img alt=\"2026 地中海抗老實踐手冊：如何在都市生活中達成 100% 橄欖多酚覆蓋 — 知橄生活 Olive Wisdom\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" data-nimg=\"fill\" class=\"object-cover group-hover:scale-105 transition-transform duration-300\" style=\"position:absolute;height:100%;width:100%;left:0;top:0;right:0;bottom:0;color:transparent\" src=\"https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1490645935967-10de6ba17061?w=1200&amp;auto=format&amp;fit=crop&amp;q=80\"/>